title: Suede
description:
One of the hugest UK bands of the 90s Suede is a bit of a mystery. Having 3 out of 5 records reaching number 1 spot on the UK album chart, the two other ones reaching number 3 and 24, still although they tried desperately thru out their career never gained any kind of recognition of a larger scale in the US reaching by never having even one song or record on top 40. With hit singles like Trash, Animal Nitrate and Electricity they made songs for a whole generation of young people to recognize them selfs in. 

Here are the five studio albums and the record Sci-Fi Lullabies consisting of b-sides and rarities.

Suede
Dog Man Star
Coming Up
Head Music
A New Morning
Sci-Fi Lullabies
